Subject: Re: For Access: Google Analytics & Google Search Console Access Allforkliftsolutions.net.au
Heath,

I hope you are doing well!!

If you can help us to get the GA & GSC access then it would be great.

The old website already had the Active GA/GSC account and Our team needs your help to get access to already installed Google Analytics(GA) & Google Search Manager(GSC) on https://allforkliftsolutions.net.au/. If you still have access to those accounts then please give admin access to gmb@zealdigital.com.au, otherwise we have to set up the new GA/GSC account. Please let me know.

Google Analytics - G-V77C9VTBHH

Google Search Console - <meta name="google-site-verification" content="UE55rz_UqfImEvLvxnYSJej0Yd9X-0J_FJn2N24eXkQ" />


Instruction for granting us access to GA & GSC. Please note the correct account IDs below:


1. Google Analytics (GA) Access -


Please grant us access to this account: G- V77C9VTBHH as follows:

- Log into your Google Analytics Account

- Navigate to the Admin icon (lower left navigation), then click on Account Access Management in the left "account" column

- Click on the blue "+" icon, then Add Users, and enter this email address:

gmb@zealdigital.com.au

- Under "Standard Roles", check the administrator option.


2. Google Search Console (GSC)Access -

- Log into your Google Search Console Account
- Click on the Setting->Users and permissions
- Click on blue Add User button-> add gmb@zealdigital.com.au
- Select the Full and click Add.




Best Regards,


Mike

Senior Project Manager
